    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/4aa907cff073c8531a8efe76440469b4.poster.avif?t=1770893784\" width=1170 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/4aa907cff073c8531a8efe76440469b4.webm?t=1770893784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Anemorie</strong></i> is a visually captivating, story-driven adventure set in the 1990s, where you step into the life of Anna—a young woman navigating the complexities of self-discovery, love, and resilience. Living with a heart condition, Anna possesses a unique gift: the ability to glimpse memories embedded in cherished objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/84673737184c4365dde2eb1fd11120dc.poster.avif?t=1770893784\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/84673737184c4365dde2eb1fd11120dc.webm?t=1770893784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/58291cb68ef4b69840fda9d0e9d5ec87.poster.avif?t=1770893784\" width=1170 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/58291cb68ef4b69840fda9d0e9d5ec87.webm?t=1770893784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>🌻 Narrative-Rich Gameplay</strong></i>: Immerse yourself in an emotional journey as Anna confronts her past, explores her supernatural abilities, and forges meaningful relationships.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>🌻 Thematic Mini-Games</strong></i><strong>:</strong> Engage in unique, context-specific mini-games that reflect Anna's experiences and challenges, offering deeper insight into her world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>🌻 Daily Activities</strong>:</i> Assist Anna with her daily routines—from cooking breakfast and journaling to bonding with her beloved cat, Kohi—each activity revealing more about her character and story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>🌻 And so much more</strong></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/0b913f4e6bf6d2a903750a682ea8d513.poster.avif?t=1770893784\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/0b913f4e6bf6d2a903750a682ea8d513.webm?t=1770893784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/cbf360494a67adea4e575e04b1ac5dcc.poster.avif?t=1770893784\" width=1170 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/cbf360494a67adea4e575e04b1ac5dcc.webm?t=1770893784\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297110/extras/b9aec583d884903571e80b15aeed0385.poster.avif?t=177089378